{
  "page": "Dwarf brother",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Faith_of_the_Seven\" title=\"Faith of the Seven\"><img alt=\"Star of the Faith.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/9/91/Star_of_the_Faith.svg/50px-Star_of_the_Faith.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/9/91/Star_of_the_Faith.svg/75px-Star_of_the_Faith.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/9/91/Star_of_the_Faith.svg/100px-Star_of_the_Faith.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Dwarf brother</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Faith_of_the_Seven\" title=\"Faith of the Seven\"><img alt=\"Star of the Faith.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/9/91/Star_of_the_Faith.svg/50px-Star_of_the_Faith.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/9/91/Star_of_the_Faith.svg/75px-Star_of_the_Faith.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/9/91/Star_of_the_Faith.svg/100px-Star_of_the_Faith.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Faith_of_the_Seven#Holy_brothers_and_sisters\" title=\"Faith of the Seven\">Brother</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiances</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Faith_of_the_Seven\" title=\"Faith of the Seven\">Faith of the Seven</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Sparrows\" title=\"Sparrows\">Sparrows</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Rivermen\" title=\"Rivermen\">Rivermen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/300_AC\" title=\"300 AC\">300&#160;AC</a><br /><a href=\"/index.php/Crownlands\" title=\"Crownlands\">Crownlands</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i> (appears)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>The <b>dwarf brother</b> is a <a href=\"/index.php/Faith_of_the_Seven#Holy_brothers_and_sisters\" title=\"Faith of the Seven\">holy brother</a> and a member of the <a href=\"/index.php/Sparrows\" title=\"Sparrows\">sparrows</a>. His given name is unknown.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Appearance_and_Character\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Appearance and Character</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Feast_for_Crows\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Appearance_and_Character\">Appearance and Character</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Dwarf_brother&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Appearance and Character\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">See also: <a href=\"/index.php/Category:Images_of_the_dwarf_brother\" title=\"Category:Images of the dwarf brother\">Images of the dwarf brother</a></div>\n<p>The <a href=\"/index.php/Dwarf\" title=\"Dwarf\">dwarf</a> is not quite five feet tall. He has a veined, bulbous nose, and his teeth are red from chewing <a href=\"/index.php/Sourleaf\" title=\"Sourleaf\">sourleaf</a>. He is dressed in the roughspun robes of a <a href=\"/index.php/Holy_brother\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Holy brother\">holy brother</a>, with the <a href=\"/index.php/Iron\" title=\"Iron\">iron</a> hammer of <a href=\"/index.php/Smith_(the_Seven)\" title=\"Smith (the Seven)\">the Smith</a> dangling down about his thick neck. He has a <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/tonsure\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:tonsure\">tonsure</a>, in the way many holy brothers cut their hair. His speech is coarse, but courteous.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Dwarf_brother&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Feast_for_Crows\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Dwarf_brother&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Feast for Crows\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>The dwarf used to serve at a holy house near <a href=\"/index.php/Maidenpool\" title=\"Maidenpool\">Maidenpool</a>, but <a href=\"/index.php/Northmen\" title=\"Northmen\">northmen</a> burned them out. They rebuilt as best they could, but <a href=\"/index.php/Sellsword\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Sellsword\">sellswords</a> came, took their pigs, burned them out and killed the brothers. He managed to survive by squeezing in the hollow of a log, hiding until the sellswords left. Afterwards, he buried his brothers, dug up a few <a href=\"/index.php/Coin\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Coin\">coins</a> the <a href=\"/index.php/Elder_Brother\" title=\"Elder Brother\">elder brother</a> had hid, and set off by himself. He went to Maidenpool, thinking he might find a <a href=\"/index.php/Ship\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Ship\">ship</a> to take him to <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a>. There he glimpsed a <a href=\"/index.php/Fool\" title=\"Fool\">fool</a> down by the docks and then later at the <a href=\"/index.php/Stinking_Goose\" title=\"Stinking Goose\">Stinking Goose</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>The dwarf brother makes <a href=\"/index.php/Brienne_of_Tarth\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Brienne of Tarth\">Brienne of Tarth</a>'s acquaintance in the common room of the <a href=\"/index.php/Seven_Swords\" title=\"Seven Swords\">Seven Swords</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/Duskendale\" title=\"Duskendale\">Duskendale</a>, courteously letting her sit down on one of the benches. She tells him that she is looking for her sister (actually <a href=\"/index.php/Sansa_Stark\" title=\"Sansa Stark\">Sansa Stark</a>), who might be accompanied by a fool (<a href=\"/index.php/Dontos_Hollard\" title=\"Dontos Hollard\">Dontos Hollard</a>). The dwarf tells Brienne that he had seen a fool at Maidenpool, and overheard <a href=\"/index.php/Dick_Crabb\" title=\"Dick Crabb\">Dick Crabb</a> boasting that he had fooled a fool and had the <a href=\"/index.php/Gold\" title=\"Gold\">gold</a> to prove it. After reassuring Brienne and finishing a bowl of crab stew bought by her, the dwarf heads for <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> \n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:You%27ve_Killed_The_Wrong_Dwarf_by_Chris_Malidore.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/dd/You%27ve_Killed_The_Wrong_Dwarf_by_Chris_Malidore.jpg/350px-You%27ve_Killed_The_Wrong_Dwarf_by_Chris_Malidore.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"235\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/dd/You%27ve_Killed_The_Wrong_Dwarf_by_Chris_Malidore.jpg/525px-You%27ve_Killed_The_Wrong_Dwarf_by_Chris_Malidore.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/d/dd/You%27ve_Killed_The_Wrong_Dwarf_by_Chris_Malidore.jpg/700px-You%27ve_Killed_The_Wrong_Dwarf_by_Chris_Malidore.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:You%27ve_Killed_The_Wrong_Dwarf_by_Chris_Malidore.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div><a href=\"/index.php/Cersei_Lannister\" title=\"Cersei Lannister\">Cersei Lannister</a> tells bounty hunters that they have killed the wrong dwarf, not <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a>. Art by Chris Malidore © Fantasy Flight Games</div></div></div>\n<p>Sometime afterwards, three men present Queen Regent <a href=\"/index.php/Cersei_Lannister\" title=\"Cersei Lannister\">Cersei Lannister</a> with a dwarf's head, grey-green and crawling with maggots. Cersei points out that the head has a bulbous nose, whereas <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a> has no nose. One of the three men says that the dwarf told them he was a <a href=\"/index.php/Sparrows\" title=\"Sparrows\">sparrow</a>, but they didn't believe him. While Cersei knows that they have killed an innocent man, she does not punish them, for fear it will discourage other such bounty hunters and allow Tyrion to escape.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc17.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc17.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> The beheaded dwarf is likely the same dwarf brother that Brienne encountered. \n</p><p>Brienne has Nimble Dick Crabb escort her to the <a href=\"/index.php/Whispers\" title=\"Whispers\">Whispers</a>, where she learns the fool observed by the dwarf brother is actually <a href=\"/index.php/Shagwell\" title=\"Shagwell\">Shagwell</a>, not Dontos.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc20.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc20.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Dwarf_brother&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>Brienne:</b> I met some other <a href=\"/index.php/Holy_brother\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Holy brother\">brothers</a> going to <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a>.<br />\n<b>Dwarf brother:</b> Aye, there's hundreds on the roads. Not only brothers. <a href=\"/index.php/Septon\" title=\"Septon\">Septons</a> too, and <a href=\"/index.php/Smallfolk\" title=\"Smallfolk\">smallfolk</a>. <a href=\"/index.php/Sparrows\" title=\"Sparrows\">Sparrows</a> all. Might be I'm a sparrow too. <a href=\"/index.php/Smith_(the_Seven)\" title=\"Smith (the Seven)\">The Smith</a>, he made me small enough.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Brienne_of_Tarth\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Brienne of Tarth\">Brienne of Tarth</a> and the dwarf brother</cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>Are you thinking of <a href=\"/index.php/Sansa_Stark\" title=\"Sansa Stark\">your sister</a>? <a href=\"/index.php/Crone_(the_Seven)\" title=\"Crone (the Seven)\">The Crone</a> will light your way to her, never fear. <a href=\"/index.php/Maiden_(the_Seven)\" title=\"Maiden (the Seven)\">The Maiden</a> will keep her safe.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;the dwarf brother, to <a href=\"/index.php/Brienne_of_Tarth\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Brienne of Tarth\">Brienne of Tarth</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>You've killed the <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">wrong</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Dwarf\" title=\"Dwarf\">dwarf</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc17.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc17.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Cersei_Lannister\" title=\"Cersei Lannister\">Cersei Lannister</a>, to the dwarf brother's killers</cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>First man:</b> This one come walking along as bold as you please, some ugly <a href=\"/index.php/Dwarf\" title=\"Dwarf\">dwarf</a>, so we thought...<br />\n<b>Second man:</b> He said he were a <a href=\"/index.php/Sparrows\" title=\"Sparrows\">sparrow</a>, and you said he was lying.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc17.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc17.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;the dwarf brother's killers</cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Dwarf_brother&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\">1.3</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\">1.4</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_9\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 9\">Chapter 9</a>, Brienne II.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc17.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc17.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc17.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\">2.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc17.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\">2.2</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_17\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 17\">Chapter 17</a>, Cersei IV.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc20.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc20.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_20\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 20\">Chapter 20</a>, Brienne IV.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404105257\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.143 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.425 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 926/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10935/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 10671/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1756/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 9/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 3053/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.250/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.47 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,call